x=6x = 6x=6 :
6 4 2 5 2 4 6 3 5 1 3 1
x=7x = 7x=7 :
6 4 2 7 2 4 6 5 3 1 7 3 5 1
所以：
if(x 是奇数) {
    [x - 1, x - 3, ..., 2, x, ..., x - 3, x - 1, 
    x - 2, x - 4, ..., 1, x, x - 4, x - 2, 1]
} else {
    [x, x - 2, ..., 2, x - 1, ..., x - 3, x - 5,
    ..., 1]
